window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>This title contains strong language and mature themes, including references to sexual violence, abuse of minors and animals, and suicide, that some listeners may find upsetting. Discretion is advised.</b></p> <p>I just met my new son-in-law . . . And he’s my ex-husband.</p> <p>They’re here. I watch them arrive from the kitchen window. My pregnant daughter and her new husband. They’ve barely known each other six months.</p> <p>I greet him with a tight smile that he recognizes as fake.</p> <p>Luke is no good for my beautiful, fragile Cerys. He’ll break her heart. I know that because he broke mine — when he was married to me.</p> <p>I don’t know what he’s after. But I’m going to make it my business to find out.</p> <p>Don’t underestimate me. I’ll do anything to keep my daughter safe.</p>"; 
